<p>2、Shazia BANO, Shaowei Li(correspondence), Chang liu, Xinxin Li, Saeed ALi. Evaluation of cyclorotation during femtosecond laser-assisted cataract surgery performed by using Lensx femtosecond laser[J]. Journal of Otolaryngology and Opthalmology of Shandong University, 2020, 34(2):47-49.</p>
